19:25.981 --> 19:29.408
(giggles)

19:29.502 --> 19:31.294
Suckers.

19:32.154 --> 19:33.838
Whoa, that was weird.

19:34.065 --> 19:35.965
Should we get the rest to go?

19:37.360 --> 19:39.826
Excuse me, I'm out of gas

19:39.846 --> 19:41.495
