19:41.514 --> 19:42.996
Would you lend me $20?

19:43.016 --> 19:44.998
I'll mail it back to you,
I promise.

19:45.092 --> 19:47.834
Uh, I'm sorry,
but that is an obvious scam.

19:47.929 --> 19:49.503
Uh, go find another sucker.

19:49.597 --> 19:52.081
Is this it-- from now on,
I live in a world

19:52.099 --> 19:55.084
