20:10.451 --> 20:12.001
(sighs)

20:14.714 --> 20:17.030
(gasps)
I knew it!

20:17.124 --> 20:18.290
Maybe you're right, baby.

20:18.443 --> 20:21.110
There still are some
good people out there.

20:21.128 --> 20:24.347
In your face, god of scams!

20:27.952 --> 20:29.285
